{
  "stem": "20581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How the hell am I going to fit in this uniform?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in Russia, you could do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You cut a little bit in here, you make it a little smaller there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So, to show you how dumb I was in that time-- so, he says to me, he says, you know what?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm going to teach you all what you have to know about it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you have to be, like-- tomorrow night, it was on a Saturday night, he said the best time to travel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because you had the, the [NON-ENGLISH], which is called the, the permit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like a furlough permit.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Right?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That you have to be back tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Otherwise, you're gonna be court-martialed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So, he says, it'll work out fine for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So, he teaches me all these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'm putting on his uniform.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I have all his papers, all stamped, everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I go into the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To military.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You gotta go in the military train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the military.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My Russian was good in that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, on a Saturday night, maybe 2:00, 3 o'clock in the morning, the train pulls in and-- to Grodno.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was the checkpoint, in Grodno.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The train pulls in, like, to a tunnel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There's only one entrance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only one person could go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, in the morning, we-- it's already-- it's also on a summer day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we coming out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, all of a sudden, the train stops.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, I'm a little guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, the military trains in that time, they didn't have no seat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just had bunks, you know, like three-stage bunk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I climbed on the top of the bunks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted to be sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I'm sitting in-- laying in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
